Apple is currently <a href="https://geni.us/classical-offer">offering a promotion</a> that provides new subscribers with a three-month free trial of <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/guide/apple-music/">Apple Music</a>, with qualified returning subscribers able to get a free two month trial.<br/>
<br/>
<img src="https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2024/08/apple-music.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-962031" /><br/>
The promotion is celebrating the release of the recent Genshin Impact album, The Shimmering Voyage Vol. 5, which is available on &zwnj;Apple Music&zwnj; and &zwnj;Apple Music&zwnj; Classical.<br/>
<br/>
&zwnj;Apple Music&zwnj; Classical includes an exclusive multi-language track-by-track commentary that accompanies the album. The commentary is voiced by the original voice actors from the game.<br/>
<br/>
Genshin Impact is an open world anime-style game that is available on iOS devices. Players control one of four interchangeable characters to complete battles, quests, and challenges for rewards. There are multiple regions to visit, each with a different musical theme built on orchestral foundations.<br/>
<br/>
